#: ../../source/export.rst:115
#: 0833bdf329074784b468c83108cfb352
msgid "Android 导出"
msgstr "Android Export"

#: ../../source/export.rst:117
#: 84fd5bed76434eb5bb755215093ea6e6
msgid "Android 比 Windows 多一步：除了插件自己的 ``libfmod_player``，还要把 FMOD 的 ``libfmod.so`` 和 ``fmod.jar`` 放进 Android 构建模板。"
msgstr ""
"Android has one extra step compared with Windows: in addition to the plugin's own ``libfmod_player`` library, you must place FMOD's ``libfmod.so`` and ``fmod.jar`` into the Android build template."

#: ../../source/export.rst:121
#: a81a8153af3147edaba35ec6b14c14ec
msgid "准备文件"
msgstr "Prepare Files"

#: ../../source/export.rst:123
#: 8477a0fa01264a03bfdde3e01c9acb83
msgid "需要准备："
msgstr "Prepare the following files:"

#: ../../source/export.rst:125
#: 311ba8e304634aa7801aeb423a35604b
msgid "``addons/fmod_player/bin/libfmod_player.android.template_release.arm64.so``"
msgstr "``addons/fmod_player/bin/libfmod_player.android.template_release.arm64.so``"

#: ../../source/export.rst:126
#: 92ea29b87d3b48f38f3623cd2a9727f9
msgid "从 FMOD Engine Android 包中取得的 ``libfmod.so``"
msgstr "``libfmod.so`` from the FMOD Engine Android package."

#: ../../source/export.rst:127
#: 51ff3497f3864d659b3fcff9012f4dda
msgid "从 FMOD Engine Android 包中取得的 ``fmod.jar``"
msgstr "``fmod.jar`` from the FMOD Engine Android package."

#: ../../source/export.rst:129
#: 6040f990367e454599765bba723abcef
msgid ""
"`为 Android 导出 <https://docs.godotengine.org/zh-cn/4.x/tutorials/export/exporting_for_android.html>`_ 如何为导出到 Android 做准备。"
msgstr ""
"`Exporting for Android <https://docs.godotengine.org/en/4.x/tutorials/export/exporting_for_android.html>`_ explains how to prepare Android exports."

#: ../../source/export.rst:132
#: 3ce43db9c4904bcd85a821f721e4c4a5
msgid "安装 Android 构建模板"
msgstr "Install the Android Build Template"

#: ../../source/export.rst:134
#: 94c5c87cb2e14d8f9163c38fab543eca
msgid "在 Godot 中执行 **项目 > 安装 Android 构建模板**。"
msgstr "In Godot, run **Project > Install Android Build Template**."

#: ../../source/export.rst:139
#: b5688c99477443409273551c869b7fc4
msgid "安装后，项目中会出现 ``res://android/build/`` 目录。"
msgstr "After installation, the project will contain a ``res://android/build/`` directory."

#: ../../source/export.rst:142
#: 23a5de33458e482d86598a8315a99fd5
msgid "复制运行库"
msgstr "Copy Runtime Libraries"

#: ../../source/export.rst:144
#: f403536a1f924839a998883adade0c71
msgid "将 Android arm64 运行库复制到 Gradle 工程的库目录。目录可以按项目需要组织， 但应保证最终 APK/AAB 中包含对应 ABI 的 ``.so`` 文件。"
msgstr ""
"Copy the Android arm64 runtime libraries into the Gradle project's library directory. The directory can be organized to fit your project, but the final APK/AAB must contain the ``.so`` files for the matching ABI."

#: ../../source/export.rst:147
#: 44f9f014192f46eeb48da3163d72f613
msgid "常见做法是放入："
msgstr "A common layout is:"

#: ../../source/export.rst:149
#: af1de94823604d50aab25cc324c3eaa1
msgid ""
"res://android/build/libs/\n"
"├── debug/\n"
"│   ├── arm64-v8a/\n"
"│   │   ├── libfmod.so\n"
"│   │   └── libfmod_player.android.template_debug.arm64.so\n"
"└── release/\n"
"    └── arm64-v8a/\n"
"        ├── libfmod.so\n"
"        └── libfmod_player.android.template_release.arm64.so"
msgstr ""
"res://android/build/libs/\n"
"├── debug/\n"
"│   ├── arm64-v8a/\n"
"│   │   ├── libfmod.so\n"
"│   │   └── libfmod_player.android.template_debug.arm64.so\n"
"└── release/\n"
"    └── arm64-v8a/\n"
"        ├── libfmod.so\n"
"        └── libfmod_player.android.template_release.arm64.so"

#: ../../source/export.rst:161
#: e0490d91c9ce446fba704645d7c8de20
msgid "实际目录可能会随 Godot 版本和模板结构不同而调整。关键是 ABI 必须匹配导出预设中的 ``arm64-v8a``。"
msgstr ""
"The exact directory may change depending on the Godot version and template structure. The key point is that the ABI must match ``arm64-v8a`` in the export preset."

#: ../../source/export.rst:165
#: 958cfe3b625541418773f7555aac8c45
msgid "添加 fmod.jar"
msgstr "Add fmod.jar"

#: ../../source/export.rst:167
#: 763aaf1ed8b34634876a376f1af27bb3
msgid "将 ``fmod.jar`` 放入："
msgstr "Place ``fmod.jar`` at:"

#: ../../source/export.rst:169
#: f0689dfbacf84a75a7f504990a6256d4
msgid "res://android/build/libs/fmod.jar"
msgstr "res://android/build/libs/fmod.jar"

#: ../../source/export.rst:173
#: bdda8fa759c74f0f96508be9dc1e0687
msgid "然后在 ``res://android/build/build.gradle`` 的 ``dependencies`` 中加入："
msgstr "Then add this to ``dependencies`` in ``res://android/build/build.gradle``:"

#: ../../source/export.rst:175
#: 777ca8b9acd44a60a6d6befff19b4cb9
msgid ""
"dependencies {\n"
"    implementation files(\"libs/fmod.jar\")\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"dependencies {\n"
"    implementation files(\"libs/fmod.jar\")\n"
"}"

#: ../../source/export.rst:182
#: 56738ca32e0f4638b0b2695192f0d720
msgid "加载 FMOD 库"
msgstr "Load the FMOD Library"

#: ../../source/export.rst:184
#: 0c1ea1c531e149b9b9e3d151deb21ec1
msgid "在 Android 启动代码中加载 FMOD 运行库。通常是在 ``GodotApp.java`` 的 ``onCreate`` 中调用："
msgstr ""
"Load the FMOD runtime library in the Android startup code. Usually this is done in ``GodotApp.java`` inside ``onCreate``:"

#: ../../source/export.rst:187
#: b8c435cc99a442c1a605f643a1ce6a39
msgid ""
"@Override\n"
"public void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {\n"
"    System.loadLibrary(\"fmod\");\n"
"    super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"@Override\n"
"public void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {\n"
"    System.loadLibrary(\"fmod\");\n"
"    super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);\n"
"}"

#: ../../source/export.rst:197
#: e742927318264e778300758cd506e256
msgid "如果你使用 FMOD 调试库，则库名可能是 ``fmodL``。发布版通常使用 ``fmod``。 不要在同一个发布构建里同时加载 ``fmod`` 和 ``fmodL``。"
msgstr ""
"If you use the FMOD debug library, the library name may be ``fmodL``. Release builds usually use ``fmod``. Do not load both ``fmod`` and ``fmodL`` in the same release build."

#: ../../source/export.rst:201
#: 4ecf2d1bf71445dd9be14aa24ecaa6f2
msgid "导出设置"
msgstr "Export Settings"

#: ../../source/export.rst:203
#: 86bd5f152bdc4031a39c77e0af98a2ad
msgid "在 Android 导出预设中选择 ``arm64-v8a``。"
msgstr "Select ``arm64-v8a`` in the Android export preset."

#: ../../source/export.rst:204
#: d36c95929e454a838e912ec1b5090daf
msgid "启用 Gradle 构建。"
msgstr "Enable Gradle Build."

#: ../../source/export.rst:209
#: dee88001614b4ae5bfc34fa6841781b3
msgid "导出 APK 或 AAB。"
msgstr "Export an APK or AAB."

#: ../../source/export.rst:210
#: c5224b2ec0444fd6b7fdbd87ba45c215
msgid "在真机上测试音频播放，不要只依赖编辑器或模拟器结果。"
msgstr "Test audio playback on a real device. Do not rely only on editor or emulator results."

#: ../../source/export.rst:213
#: 45b14a8874684e7a99f562e4f17a0842
msgid "源码构建发布库"
msgstr "Build Release Libraries from Source"

#: ../../source/export.rst:215
#: 6a1fdbeedd3647a0bdd4816fd1c6d7d7
msgid "如果你修改了插件 C++ 源码，需要重新构建平台二进制。"
msgstr "If you modified the plugin C++ source code, rebuild the platform binaries."

#: ../../source/export.rst:217
#: feccc40e907644baa1cd61790ae1d9b0
msgid "Windows release："
msgstr "Windows release:"

#: ../../source/export.rst:219
#: ba946cf4af4c48b3b3a085632cc7d9b8
msgid "scons platform=windows target=template_release arch=x86_64"
msgstr "scons platform=windows target=template_release arch=x86_64"

#: ../../source/export.rst:223
#: de817f00d1c54f0badcf581dbeae64ca
msgid "Android release："
msgstr "Android release:"

#: ../../source/export.rst:225
#: 1e247f217f09438c9996e3fd68bc711d
msgid "scons platform=android target=template_release arch=arm64"
msgstr "scons platform=android target=template_release arch=arm64"

#: ../../source/export.rst:229
#: 5794b50b04d54becaf4b01058b85b60d
msgid "构建完成后，将生成的二进制复制到 ``addons/fmod_player/bin/``，并确认 ``fmod_player.gdextension`` 中的文件名一致。"
msgstr ""
"After building, copy the generated binaries into ``addons/fmod_player/bin/`` and make sure the filenames match ``fmod_player.gdextension``."

#: ../../source/export.rst:233
#: 93c769dc27aa478a97dfd8f17afbc305
msgid "导出排错"
msgstr "Export Troubleshooting"

#: ../../source/export.rst:236
#: 98d1810bbf7b4e798ee81a1fcee73408
msgid "Windows 常见问题"
msgstr "Common Windows Issues"

#: ../../source/export.rst:238
#: 03e19c03437948d88bf41f524510a19f
msgid "**导出后启动失败或提示找不到 GDExtension**"
msgstr "**The exported game fails to start or reports that GDExtension cannot be found**"

#: ../../source/export.rst:240
#: f3082ef0027648e495d28d6b49bc0259
msgid "确认 ``fmod_player.gdextension`` 被包含在导出包中。"
msgstr "Make sure ``fmod_player.gdextension`` is included in the export package."

#: ../../source/export.rst:241
#: 5328e0130cc7449794a74b2f094cebcd
msgid "确认 release 版本的 ``fmod_player.windows.template_release.x86_64.dll`` 存在。"
msgstr "Make sure the release version of ``fmod_player.windows.template_release.x86_64.dll`` exists."

#: ../../source/export.rst:242
#: b796f34b112e4c0f94972005f39c81a7
msgid "确认导出架构为 ``x86_64``。"
msgstr "Make sure the export architecture is ``x86_64``."

#: ../../source/export.rst:243
